      "content": "For high-level boardroom meetings, your attire should be impeccably tailored and conservative, favoring classic silhouettes in rich, muted colors. Attention to detail, such as polished shoes and subtle, high-quality accessories, conveys meticulousness and control. Ensure your grooming is neat and understated—think clean hair, minimal makeup, and well-maintained hands—to project an aura of effortless authority. This polished presentation supports your expertise without distracting the focus from your insights.",
