      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For a woman with thick, natural textured hair, sleek, polished styling that showcases the health and quality of the hair, perhaps in a controlled high-up style, works well to maintain formality. Regarding a woman wearing a hijab, the key is ensuring the fabric is structured, neatly draped, and monochromatic to complement the professional suit rather than compete with it. In both cases, the goal is seamless integration: the grooming element supports the professional ensemble rather than acting as a focal point.",
      "source": "target",
